# AI generation rules
- Input sources: transcript + optional user notes + platform + language.
- Output must be deterministic in structure:
  - title
  - description
  - hashtags (array)
  - optional chapters/timestamps (if requested)
- Never hallucinate facts: if transcript doesn't support a claim, don't include it.
- Keep platform-specific export templates separate (YouTube vs TikTok vs Instagram).
